Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 不會弄疼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吸我的血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吸的啦 你的血什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的毒注入你體內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 毒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的毒注入你體內
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你永遠離不開我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(394,434)}魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 不會弄疼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 你就離不開我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.26,0:01:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是生還是死 都永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.89,0:01:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做好覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺…覺悟什麼的我還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我已經施下詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 你就是我的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的護衛 我最親愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你突然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別計較了 大兔也說愛我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣魔法就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(397,437)}毒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 你討厭我？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解到世界和構築我身體的一切都改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(471,434)}毒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 我的故事開始了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才對呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔 我說大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我說 該醒醒了大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 班會早就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:49.49,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(500,500)\be10\pos(617,122)}「放學後的900秒（前篇）」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙嗎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼了啊 大兔你也真是的 從第五節課一直睡到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師怎麼叫都醒不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班會已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嘛 大兔沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 我今天睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 你做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有口水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.12,0:03:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口水…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.92,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好火熱呀 咻咻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.77,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆 果然是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:29.98,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙明明是我的老婆的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 那啥…我們不是那種關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這種事還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那種關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別這麼遲鈍好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你 睡了這麼久還是睏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔不會是病了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事 我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳呢 還疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了遙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實最近我一直做同一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你 你絕對會笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼 不是很讓人在意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證不笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那我就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候的我 被一個女生告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說「我愛你 大兔」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常做的夢就是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是保證不笑的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 因為實在是太可笑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是很多年前的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 難道說是遙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能 我還沒向大兔表白過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 那女生超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思 太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是月光大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光大人 月光大人 看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光大人 接下來是學生會的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事 雜魚 不要進入我的視野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了 也請向我說些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事 礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說月光 可以把這些傢伙都打飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做多餘的事 渣滓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是渣滓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:03.66,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光大人 工作請多多加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學業優秀 運動萬能 超受女生歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一入高中就當上學生會長的超級新星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅月光大人經過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔因為紅君受歡迎 所以很羨慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你真的想受歡迎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不想受歡迎是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我不是那樣的超人 像那樣受歡迎是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙也是 覺得交往的話還是那種傢伙比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可說不準
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙其實還真是可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的僕人 我的護衛 我最親愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 或許因為睡太多了 有點頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 那傢伙剛才有在看我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅君嗎 是大兔的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 總覺得剛我被玩味的盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種人每天都在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的平凡人生完全相反的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔才不平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很平凡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不是了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那你覺得「平凡不是很好嗎」如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果每天都能安寧的微笑 就再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了 今天有網球部的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 大兔 你能等我結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好無情 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平凡也許確實不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高一就說這種話 總覺得有些像老頭子就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔爺爺 回家路上要小心車哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平凡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常走路沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但劇烈運動就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於因為受傷而失去了至今努力的一切的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是在我身邊向我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著「沒事的 沒事的」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入同一所高中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什麼也不做的我的身邊 今天也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果每天都能安寧的微笑 就再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 得找點事來做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吻我啊 月光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴？你叫我閉嘴是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.44,0:09:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你有在聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點吻我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 月光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了 快點吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要沒命了 我真的要沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了 要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 月光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 雜魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶劍破邪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(392,432)}SpellError
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊 月光 很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接吻這種程度的對手也無法打倒嗎 雜魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是雜魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是囉嗦的雜魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我口渴了 想喝Dr.cinnamon 能去買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單純的笨蛋 隨你便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我會連月光的一起買回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了 月光要喝什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這摘要真是糟糕透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:24.65,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於上古魔法師賽托希梅亞\N犧者鐵大兔\N還有紅月光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dr.cinnamon Dr.cinnamon 明明這麼好喝卻沒什麼人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 是剛才跟紅月光一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃開！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…遙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不肯過來…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直一個人在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點…來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再等一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一次5分鐘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說和我在一起很開心的大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和大兔在一起也非常幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:14:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有大兔不是為了利用我或得到我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說和我在一起很開心 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔 好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大兔把我忘記了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔現在活得很幸福的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被忘記了也就被忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是假話 請不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要忘記我 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你內褲完全走光了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 那個難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 你為啥還活著 是人頭妖？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 話說那邊倒著的難道是我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果…果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋都掉下來了還會覺得身體疼 太怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我能動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 怎麼回事 這是什麼構造讓他能動起來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那樣 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是變形機器人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那算什麼反應？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪…怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肇事逃逸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿手機拍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NICE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見不死身君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先把頭 先把頭裝上…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接上了 已經沒事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪兒都不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿也能全力奔跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…是大兔終於肯死去一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…這樣就終於完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,900秒的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 記起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣我所有的力量就終於能回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的 剛剛的聲音是夢裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識…我從很久以前就認識她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是生還是死 都永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽托希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於肯想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會來接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在這個樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要改變才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…現在是6歲的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了9年左右就是15歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔會誇我可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是不誇就殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這數不清的歲月中希梅亞一直在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我絕不會忘記 絕對會去救希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼我忘掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這是希梅亞賦予我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞 我們約定了絕不分開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會保護好希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個公園 在曾經只有我們兩人玩耍的那個公園
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒變 總是詭異的沒有其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:22:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我為什麼認為希梅亞會等在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了！來得太晚了 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等五分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這9年間 我一直在想著再等五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來的話絕對殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是 一直以來都…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9年間一直？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著再等五分鐘 再等五分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我明明有約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你來了 原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被無數複雜原因糾纏著的我們的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:24:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的故事 都向著目的地開始進發
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.45,0:24:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著渣滓們 我是學生會會長紅月光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.87,0:24:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有從今天起你們全員一生都是我的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.13,0:24:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻跪下致敬 為你這份幸運激動的顫抖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.45,0:24:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們面前的是真真正正的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.23,0:24:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 不服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.11,0:24:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不服的站出來砍掉 剩下的全是我的奴隸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:34.84,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fade(250,250)}追憶の果てに静かに揺らめく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:42.21,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fade(250,250)}永遠に包む遥かの約束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:50.54,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fade(250,250)}悲しみに濡れた空蝉壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:58.93,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fade(250,250)}絶望を掏り替えて孤独は目立ってた
